In collaboration with digital collage artist, Slimesunday, we present: 

“That's Nifty”

a podcast that features a prominent digital artist and his two run of the mill NFT (Non-Fungible Token) collectors interviewing figures in the NFT Art space.  They don't always know what is going on, but they know it's nifty. Moments captured here will document the rising tide surrounding the NFT Space as it enters the zeitgeist.

